com.io7m.jregions.core.unparameterized.volumes

Class VolumeL.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.jregions.core.unparameterized.volumes.VolumeL.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    VolumeL

    public static final class VolumeL.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type VolumeL. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
